<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ההזמנה כבר נוצרה</title>

    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a2351 0%, #1e3a6f 50%, #2d4a7c 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: pulse 15s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%,100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 60px 50px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            max-width: 550px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            animation: slideIn 0.6s ease-out;
            border-top: 6px solid #ff9800;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from { opacity:0; transform: translateY(-40px); }
            to { opacity:1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .warning-icon {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffb74d 0%, #f57c00 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.4);
            border: 5px solid #fff3e0;
            font-size: 60px;
            color: white;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #0a2351;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container { padding: 40px 30px; }
            h1 { font-size: 26px; }
            p { font-size: 16px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="warning-icon">⚠️</div>

    <h1>ההזמנה כבר נוצרה</h1>

    <p>המשלוח יישלח לנקודת החלוקה שבחרת.</p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
